00:07:59.680 --> 00:08:01.740
But from the origins
of the company,

00:08:01.740 --> 00:08:03.200
everyone worked remotely.

00:08:03.200 --> 00:08:04.850
So it's built into the culture.

00:08:04.850 --> 00:08:06.710
That every new hire
it's assumed you

00:08:06.710 --> 00:08:08.990
will work from anywhere on
the planet that you wish.

00:08:08.990 --> 00:08:12.000
It does not matter,
nobody cares.

00:08:12.000 --> 00:08:15.810
The company is
naturally very diverse.

00:08:15.810 --> 00:08:17.990
Geographically and in
terms of time zones.

00:08:17.990 --> 00:08:19.930
There's people working
in every time zone.

00:08:19.930 --> 00:08:21.680
So at any time, no matter
where you are in the world

00:08:21.680 --> 00:08:24.230
or what time zone you're in,
you can log into the chatroom

00:08:24.230 --> 00:08:26.146
