going to be online

00:08:46.390 --> 00:08:48.181
and where they're going
to be working from.

00:08:51.580 --> 00:08:53.835
They use what's called,
the fancy word for it

00:08:53.835 --> 00:08:55.154
is continuous deployment.

00:08:55.154 --> 00:08:57.070
So another reason why
they're able to get away

00:08:57.070 --> 00:08:59.060
with so much autonomy
is that WordPress.com

00:08:59.060 --> 00:09:00.790
is a live service.

00:09:00.790 --> 00:09:02.690
And they have very
few restrictions

00:09:02.690 --> 00:09:04.650
about how features launch.

00:09:04.650 --> 00:09:06.640
So if you're a
designer or developer,

00:09:06.640 --> 00:09:08.310
