for features, or how

00:09:10.520 --> 00:09:12.680
you decide what bugs you're
going to fix this week,

00:09:12.680 --> 00:09:14.600
it's very self-directed.

00:09:14.600 --> 00:09:16.460
And autonomous.

00:09:16.460 --> 00:09:19.680
Which means that there's never a
large dependencies between code

00:09:19.680 --> 00:09:20.540
bases.

00:09:20.540 --> 00:09:22.560
There's very rarely
a huge schedule

00:09:22.560 --> 00:09:25.020
that's going to block
some work from being done.

00:09:25.020 --> 00:09:27.040
Which eliminates a lot
of the normal politics

00:09:27.040 --> 00:09:28.855
